        #
        # InterfaceStatus:
        #
        # Current state | first state  |  CacheTimer
        # -----------------------------------------
        # up              up              $gShortCacheTimer
        # up              down            0
        # down            down            $gLongCacheTimer
        # down            up              0
        # other           *               0
        # *               other           0
        #
        # One exception to that logic is the "Changed" flag. If this
